    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out per MRL 2 requirements. Mesh independence GCI of 3.2% and experimental validation MARE of 8.4% provide high confidence in model predictions. The CFD model is deemed credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. RH < 1.0 across all five evaluated operating conditions supports regulatory submission.",
